* {{topt|Can you tell me about the Jubbly Jive?}}
** '''Player:''' Can you tell me about the Jubbly Jive?
** '''Gurtob:''' Dis wat Gurtob best at! Dancin' wif da jubblies.
** '''Ros:''' He's right, you know. Whilst exploring the ocean, a group of Barracudas saw Gurtob 'sailing' around this place on what could barely be described as a boat, hunting jubblies.
** '''Gurtob:''' Dey join in and try steal Gurtob jub jubs! But creatures nice and give Gurtob strong boatsie. Now Gurtob friends.
** '''Ros:''' Gurtob friends indeed! When the Barracudas tried it themselves, they realised how much fun it was sailing around these tight spaces. They worked with Gurtob to design this trial!
** '''Gurtob:''' Gurtob make bestest trial back then! Now yous little creatures make it easier, but me think it still best.
** '''Ros:''' It's true that some claim the trial is easier now than before due to new pathways being carved through the fetid pools. Still, don't let that fool you! The course is still a tricky one!
** '''Player:''' So what do I need to do during the trial?
** '''Gurtob:''' Go da fastest, grab da toadies, throw da toadies, trick da jubblies, eat da jubblies. Dat's it.
** '''Ros:''' Let me explain it in non-Gurtob terms...
** '''Ros:''' The goal of this trial is to use balloon toads to lure jubblies. First up, you'll want to sail west to collect da... sorry, collect the balloon toads from a boat of ours.
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|Who are you?}}
** '''Player:''' Who are you?
** '''Gurtob:''' Me's Gurtob. Da fastest jubbly hunter on boatsies and big boss of dis boatsie skill test.
** '''Ros:''' And I'm Ros. I'm fairly new to the Barracudas and I help Gurtob out with managing this trial.
** '''Ros:''' He's not much of a speaker and is easily misunderstood, so I help translate and make sure that any up and coming prospective Barracudas understand exactly what they need to do.
** '''Player:''' Why stay out here in this awful smelling place? Aren't there better places to be at sea?
** '''Gurtob:''' Dis Gurtob home. Only funny smelly is you's scrawny creatures.
** '''Gurtob:''' Gurtob find funny when you's creatures gets stucks in bubbly watery. Gurtob also likes when you's creatures bring da jubblies.
** '''Player:''' I get what's in it for him, but what's in it for you, Ros?
** '''Ros:''' Well, after joining the Barracudas, I discovered a fascination for different cultures. This is just a small step in my personal journey to understand more about the world!
** '''Ros:''' Plus da jubblies do taste good!
** '''Gurtob:''' Da jubblies do taste da bestest.
** {{tact|other}}
* {{topt|Who are the Barracudas?}}
** '''Player:''' Who are the Barracudas?
** '''Gurtob:''' Dey like da creatures which sound like da fishies but no taste like da fishes but fast like da fastest fishies.
** '''Player:''' Erm...
** '''Ros:''' Gurtob sure has a way with words!
** '''Ros:''' Us Barracudas are the fastest sailors across the entire ocean! Our motto is 'Anyone from anywhere as long as they can sail.'
** '''Ros:''' We work together to help hone each other's skills and test our mettle through challenges called Barracuda Trials.
** '''Player:''' Can I become a Barracuda?
** '''Ros:''' Of course you can! There's a bunch of trial masters like Gurtob scattered across the seas. Best our trials and earn your spot in our ranks.
** {{tact|other}}
* {{topt|I'd best be off.}}
** '''Player:''' I'd best be off.
** {{tact|end}}

